00:37:57.390 --> 00:37:58.390
&gt;&gt;female #1: Um-hum.

00:37:58.390 --> 00:38:02.540
&gt;&gt;Miguel del Valle: Chicago police officers
should live in the City of Chicago and it

00:38:02.540 --> 00:38:07.280
should be a requirement and should continue
to be a requirement. A couple of my opponents

00:38:07.280 --> 00:38:11.630
have said, "Yeah, it's something we can talk
about." What are we -- we're tryin' to build

00:38:11.630 --> 00:38:15.110
up the middle class in every neighborhood
in the City of Chicago. We're gonna allow

00:38:15.110 --> 00:38:21.820
people to move out but earn their salary from
property tax payers and residents in the City

00:38:21.820 --> 00:38:25.320
of Chicago who pay taxes? So that's wrong.

00:38:25.320 --> 00:38:31.490
Community policing. One of my problems with
Jody Weis is that he really hasn't strengthened

00:38:31.490 --> 00:38:36.610
the CAPS Program. So I wanna reinvent the
