00:38:36.610 --> 00:38:42.220
policing model that's effective. And I understand
that there were budget cuts this year that

00:38:42.220 --> 00:38:47.681
pulled police officers away from community
policing. That has to be reversed. We have

00:38:47.681 --> 00:38:54.110
to move folks from administrative positions
and free those positions up for the front

00:38:54.110 --> 00:38:56.280
line. That has to happen.

00:38:56.280 --> 00:39:02.630
