00:39:33.650 --> 00:39:39.740
instances, there were shootings practically
in front of the camera that should have been

00:39:39.740 --> 00:39:44.340
captured, and each time I checked, either
the camera was not working properly, it was

00:39:44.340 --> 00:39:53.900
not turned on, or it wasn't facing the right
direction because it scans. And so I was and

00:39:53.900 --> 00:39:59.150
have been dissatisfied with some of Jody Weis'
responses.

