gonna pay him as much as he's makin' now.

00:40:32.680 --> 00:40:39.300
But I prefer to have my own team. I'm gonna
be held accountable as mayor, I want my own

00:40:39.300 --> 00:40:44.240
superintendent in the Chicago Public Schools,
who by the way is an educator. And for the

00:40:44.240 --> 00:40:50.340
police department I feel that we should be
able to find someone within the ranks who

00:40:50.340 --> 00:40:55.000
can assume that position. And I think that
will do a lot for morale.

